#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:70
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find Purple Beard staring into space at the ship's biggest window. He "
"turns to look at you as you enter the room. You are about to speak but his "
"expression catches you for a moment. It is as if the weight of the "
"multiverse is on his shoulders. \"Blow it up.\" He speaks with gravitas that"
" makes you flinch. Without saying another word he leaves the room, leaving "
"you alone with your thoughts."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:73
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:79
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_JON\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I... I can't believe my eyes! Have you *seen* how advanced the Obelisk drones were?! Just the sight of them in combat got my wheels churning for a potential drone booster design 2.0!\" Jon grins ear to ear, barely being able to contain his enthusiasm.\t\n"
"\t\n"
"\tHis mood suddenly drops as he realizes the choice you have been presented with. \"Friend, if there is one thing I learned while working in Wentworth Innovations, it's that there is ALWAYS another way to solve a problem, no matter how difficult it may seem. I know this war is taking countless lives every second, but I truly believe this doesn't need to be the only way. If you detonate that bomb, then any potential third option will be forever lost... I won't stop you of course, but please, be absolutely sure this is what you want, alright?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:84
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_JON\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:90
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_DAISY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Yes! We did it! We beat the exterminators! I... I can't believe my own sensors. This truly feels like a dream! And for me to have been in the forefront... to have brought my people's name into the history books... It almost... makes me feel worthy of being who I am again. After being destroyed in such an abject manner only to be resurrected by an alien of such... unique anatomy and goals... I thought I was a failure, but...\"\n"
"\n"
"\tDaisy spends a few moments collecting her thoughts before giving you the Obelisk equivalent of a smile. \"Thank you... what do they call your type again? Renegade? No, that's too formal. Thank you... Friend.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:96
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_DAISY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_VANCE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"To be frank, I'm not sure I deserve to be alive after all of this. Sure, "
"that wasn't me, I suppose, but... I shared the same blood as that man! I'm a"
" exact copy of him! What makes me special enough to be allowed to live? If "
"you want to know what I think, I say let's activate that bomb, and let the "
"Multiverse forget about all of us and this petty war, once and for all!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:105
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_VANCE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:111
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_LEAH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Ahahahaaaa! You saw the size of that thing, right!? It put every last "
"flagship I've seen to shame.\" Leah's voice lowers, the staunch Rebel "
"seemingly apprehensive all of a sudden. \"You didn't disappoint me either, "
"beyatch... good on you. You're the best rival I've ever had, and it'd be a "
"shame if our arcs ended here...\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:114
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_LEAH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:120
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_SAMMY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I... I don't know what to say, Renegade. All I wanted was to go home and "
"you decided to drag me through this... I've seen hell with my own eyes, and "
"it's made of cubes! For the love of God, please tell me that you don't plan "
"on blowing all of us up! I don't want to die!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:123
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_SAMMY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:129
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_STEFAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"This is all madness! Cube people. Multiversal bombs. None of it makes any "
"sense! I just want to go back to selling my minelaunchers. Do whatever you "
"want with that... thing! I'm the last person who should have a say on "
"this.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:132
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_STEFAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:138
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_GOZER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Well done, kid. Looks like you've passed with flying colors. Consider "
"yourself officially recruited into the Haunts. Now, I won't tell you what to"
" do with that little bomb, but I'm sure you'll agree that the opportunity to"
" work with us is quite lucrative and it'd be such a shame to pass it up...\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:142
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_GOZER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:148
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_CYRA\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I'm not sure what to think, Renegade. Seeing a man I respected so much be "
"willing to do something so horrible... It's not something I think I'll ever "
"be able to fully accept. As for my advice? Don't let this be how your "
"journey ends. Destroy that infernal device, please!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:151
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_CYRA\"]/choice/text"
