"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_Y\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance's eye twitches before he suddenly turns off the video call. Y then "
"turns around and returns to her post, clearly proud of what she just did."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:300
