#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:375
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance pauses, and appears on the vidscreen. Both Tully and Jerry step forwards. Vance stares in utter disbelief, seeing the two most important people in his life standing in front of him. Jerry is the first to speak up.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\"Uncle...please! I know it's not too late. It's never too late! Put down that bomb, and...and we'll talk.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:379
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:381
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance looks away and closes his eyes. He sighs deeply, speaking with regret "
"in his voice. 'No! It's far too late for that. Jerry...Brodric...I'm sorry.'"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:383
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:385
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Tully steps in, nearly filling the screen with his presence. He begins to tear up, a mixture of rage, sadness, and righteous fire filling his eyes.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Vance! For the love of God, stop this madness! You see the death and the misery you've sowed! Trillions, maybe even quadrillions of innocents have died because of the Rebellion - how many more will have to fall before you're finally satisfied!? You may never be able to fully atone for your actions, but you can still fix your mistakes, leave a positive impact on the Multiverse! I'm here for you. Jerry's here for you. We can help. Please... stand down.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:389
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:391
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance is frozen in place. His legendarily stoic demeanor finally seems to break, and the Admiral of the Rebellion begins to tear up. The video feed cuts out as you hear the sound of a teleporter sending someone in... against all odds, you've managed to convince him to hand over the bomb, and he does so without looking anybody in the eyes.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tJerry opens his arms for a hug, which catches the Admiral off guard. He takes it, simply remaining silent for a few moments, before speaking up. \"I-I'm trusting you, Jerry... please, don't let me make another mistake...\" Behind him, as he breaks from the embrace, he finds Tully offering him a handshake. After a moment of deliberation, he clasps Tully's hand in his own, ready to make things right."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:395
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Vance Prime"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:397
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TULLY_AND_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:409
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly, the video feed turns on again. On the other side of the camera is "
"the cloning bay of the capital ship, which leaves everyone confused for a "
"moment. Another Vance steps out of the clonebay, the machine fully gearing "
"him up before everyone's eyes. He hisses with unbridled fury, brandishing "
"his energy-axe. \"TRAITOR!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:411
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:413
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Tully, Jerry, and Vance Prime collectively drop their jaws in shock at the "
"new sight. Vance Prime desperately tries to teleport back, to no avail. "
"\"What have you done?\" MFK Aces begin to surround the cloned Vance, "
"saluting their new leader. \"Kissing the Federation's ass after so long? We "
"don't allow rats like you within our glorious ranks. I may not have your "
"little bomb, but once Universe 1 gets ahold of all of this Obelisk "
"technology, I'm certain we can make something much, muuuuuch worse.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:415
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:417
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The new Vance's glare narrows to something sharp, hateful, utterly violent. "
"Every word out of his mouth is akin to the venom of a snake, all of his old "
"fire reigniting in a concentrated blaze. \"You...you DARE to insult me with "
"THIS!? After everything you, and me, and every other Vance across the "
"Multiverse has done to build a brighter future, you come craaaaawling back "
"to the very same force that crushed your spirit so long ago? And now, you "
"lick their boots, and beg for forgiveness, running away from every "
"responsibility you've ever had, every wonderful opportunity, and leave all "
"of your men without a leader, all of your friends and family without the "
"father and uncle they need!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:419
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:421
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry tries to speak up, but he's cut off by the clone. \"Oh, don't come "
"crying to me, you spoiled little shit... no family member of mine throws "
"their lot in with the Feds and expects me to think of them as my blood.\" "
"Tully jumps in, attempting to defend Jerry, but the feed is cut before he "
"can say anything."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:423
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:425
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry collapses to his knees, shocked and speechless as how easily he was betrayed. \"I should have known...\" Jerry chokes up a sob, and holds his head in his hands while tears form puddles on the ground. Vance Prime is fuming in the background, exhibiting much the same anger as his clone at being chewed out for going back on his mistakes. He steps over to his nephew...\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"That scumbag over there is a liar. You're a Wentworth, Jerry, and nothing will ever take that away from you. Certainly not the decree of some Multiversal tyrant.\" He contains his anger for a moment, offering Jerry a hand."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:430
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry is still recovering from what happened, but he seems to have gotten an"
" idea."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:433
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:435
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_TWIST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry staggers to his feet, embracing Vance one more time before wiping away"
" his tears. \"Well, there's only one thing left to do now.\" He draws out a "
"massive Gatling gun. You aren't sure where he got it from, but you don't "
"have the time to question it. Vance pulls out his axe, its blade crackling "
"to life as he stands beside his nephew, ready to put an end to this saga."

