#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:562
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance Prime steps into view, causing the Vance on the other side to eye him "
"with pure disgust. \"Oh, and just when I thought the Rebels couldn't stoop "
"any lower, before me stands a living testament to why joining the Feds was "
"the best decision I ever made. You are a pathetic excuse for a leader, "
"Vance. Too much of a coward to fight and die like the trillions of good "
"soldiers who serve you unconditionally, yet too prideful to admit that "
"everything you've done was so, so wrong.\""

