msgstr ""
"Vance Prime gazes into the camera, his stoic expression shattered into a "
"stare of absolute, pure, focused rage. You're concerned he might pop a blood"
" vessel in his brain from how tightly his face is clenched. After a while of"
" awkward silence, he simply turns away from the camera, refusing to look at "
"his doppelganger. \"...oh, you snake. You are going to regret everything you"
" have ever done for these last few minutes of your pitiful life.\""

