"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The other Vance simply laughs at the threat, triggering the artilleries and "
"the Multiverse drive once more. \"Oh, we will see about that... you dirty "
"little rat.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:578
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:590
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance One steps into view, causing Vance Prime to eye him with pure hatred. "
"\"Well well well, if it isn't my older form, still chasing the dragon that "
"is the Paragon? Come on Prime, we both know you are only doing this out of a"
" sense of obligation to your man. Admit it, you lost that spark years ago!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:592
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:594
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Prime's glare narrows to something sharp, hateful, utterly violent. "
"Every word out of his mouth is akin to the venom of a snake, all of his old "
"fire reigniting in a concentrated blaze. \"You...you DARE to insult me with "
"THIS!? After I SAVED you and your weak rebellion from collapsing all those "
"years ago?! I'm the reason you are alive! I gave you the best position you "
"could ever ask for, a god among man, and THIS is how you thank me?!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:596
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:598
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Vance One gazes into the camera, a malicious grin across his face. \"Oh, "
"Prime...How i will enjoy breaking your neck under my boots.\" He laughs and "
"turns around, ignoring Prime, who seems to be almost boiling over with rage."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:600
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:602
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SHOWDOWN_VANCE_ONE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Prime opens his mouth to speak, but stops at the last second. Shaking with "
"rage, he triggers the artilleries and the Multiverse drive once more."

